A "rescue mission" went horribly bad for popular Pastor Paseka "Mboro" Motsoeneng when he got nabbed recently for speeding on his way to a praying expedition. The charismatic pastor, known for his controversial stunts and long nails which he claims are the source of his healing powers, confirmed to Sunday World that he was caught doing 131km/h on a regional road in Thaba Nchu in the Free State. TO READ MORE ON THIS STORY GET A COPY OF TODAY'S SUNDAY WORLD